How can I write an SQL query to find all instructors in the "Comp. Sci." department who have a salary greater than $70,000?
```sql
SELECT name
FROM instructor
WHERE dept_name = 'Comp. Sci.' AND salary > 70000;
```
This query will retrieve the names of all instructors in the "Comp. Sci." department whose salary is greater than $70,000.
